The physically stored information potential, B’gen, enters the experiment, where entropy-generating, destructive processes erase information at rate B’eras(ed). B′ is the net information potential accumulation rate. The net information potential accumulation rate, B′ (Eq. 3):3B’=B’gen−B’eras\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
